{"tid":1672324,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"民間發起下周六集會 警方質疑維園能否容納大量集會人士","createTime":"2019-10-24T04:47:33.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-24T09:21:35.000Z","uid":184679,"like":12,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":22,"replies":[{"pid":"4dc7ffef6421111646ddbd261fa72960160faf6a","tid":1672324,"uid":184679,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-24T04:47:33.000Z","msg":"【Now新聞台】民間發起下星期六在維園舉行集會，主題是堅守香港人自治權，向國際發出求援訊息。集會申請人劉頴匡與警方開會商討，他會後引述，警方質疑維園能否容納到集會人數。<br />\n<br />\n劉頴匡：「一方面擔心人數太多的話，會否對秩序有影響，或者場地容納不到。我們提出人數多的話，會以流水式進行集會，呼籲場內人士先離開，讓更多人進入場地，我們與警方作出此提議。第二他們擔心場地問題，維園是否會批出場地進行合法集會，就這點會與康文署保持密切溝通。」<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.now.com/home/local/player?newsId=367389&amp;refer=\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.now.com%2Fhome%2Flocal%2Fplayer%3FnewsId%3D367389%26refer%3D&d=pzn6Hq8jxzH2PmSSbZvUof%2FZYLwdGiEzwb2OZuYF8yg%3D&h=bec807f8\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.now.com%2Fhome%2Flocal%2Fplayer%3FnewsId%3D367389%26refer%3D&h=3a71c26d\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.now.com/home/local/player?newsId=367389&amp;refer=</a>"},{"pid":"a07f172adbbdf092871be15eda595a83ba6949b5","tid":1672324,"uid":33930,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-24T04:47:53.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>【SUCK／1026】長龍爆買日 - 黃店存貨壓力測試（2）<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1672101\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1672101</a><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/4Sw3aYY.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F4Sw3aYY.jpg&h=18631120&s={SIZE}\" /></blockquote>"},{"pid":"189b561b3959479e6cc743d52abbc6a692ed2947","tid":1672324,"uid":2607,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-24T04:49:13.000Z","msg":"Pish"},{"pid":"ae4bd8e9175ff6e13096f08794949f82ad0351d8","tid":1672324,"uid":184679,"like":5,"dislike":1,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-24T04:49:33.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://encrypted-tbn0.gstatic.com/image